file.title: AMM PART II-1285 - CHAPTER 21-21-02-06 - COCKPIT AIR CONDITIONING OUTLETS - INSPECTION/CHECK

page.data: AIRCRAFT MAINTENANCE MANUAL COCKPIT AIR CONDITIONING OUTLETS - INSPECTION/CHECK EFFECTIVITY: ALL 1. General A. This section gives the procedures to inspect the conditioned air outlets in the cockpit. B. The procedures in this section are given in the sequence below. The tasks identified with ( ♦) are part of the Scheduled Maintenance Requirements Document (SMRD).
